name: Google I/O Extended 2023 by GDG Cloud Kolkata
description: Google I/O Extended is an annual event organized by Google that takes place alongside the main Google I/O conference. It is designed to bring the Google I/O experience to developers and technology enthusiasts who cannot attend the main event in person. The purpose of Google I/O Extended is to foster a sense of community, share knowledge, and provide access to the latest technologies.
